= Implementation

The implementation prototype was written in a hybrid environment combining Rust-based simulation kernels with Python orchestration scripts.

== Example Rust Module

```rust
pub struct SensorNode {
    pub id: usize,
    pub energy: f64,
    pub neighbors: Vec<usize>,
}

impl SensorNode {
    pub fn update(&mut self, dt: f64) {
        let drain = 0.015 * dt;
        self.energy = (self.energy - drain).max(0.0);
    }

    pub fn active(&self) -> bool {
        self.energy > 0.1
    }
}
```
